name: First General Meeting
description: This is our first general meeting for Spring 2024. Join us for checking out future events, networking, and more!

name: Ice-Breaker Event
description: This is our second general meeting for Spring 2024. Join us for fun games and connections with like-minded peers

name: Tackle the Titanic Data Set (Part 1)
description: Join us for a special event where we dive into the Titanic dataset! We'll split into groups, explore Kaggle, and guide you through the tools needed for data exploration.

name: Tackle the Titanic Data Set (Part 2)
description: Join us again for the continuation of previous meeting where we explore and analyze the Titanic dataset to boost our Python skills. This meeting will demonstrate data visualization.

name: Social Meet-up
description: Join us at the game room to have fun, ask questions, play games, and hang out with fellow members. Snacks will be provided!
location: Games Room @ Bronco Student Center (Building 35, Room 1110)

name: Data Analytics Competition
description: Team up with peers, answer questions, and compete with other teams to tackle various problems in Data Analytics. There are prizes for the first place winner!

name: Webinar: Masters Program
description: Interested in graduate degree in Data Science? If you are, check out this important meeting where UC Berkeley is hosting a webinar presenting on their data science masters program!

name: Tackle the Titanic Data Set (Part 3)
description: Join us again for the continuation of previous meeting about tackling the Titanic dataset. This time, we will primarily focus on the machine learning portion of analysis to build a ML model.
